ence-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-1-valensole\">1. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/valensole\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Valensole<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Valensole is the capital of the lavender region of Provence: a small, charming village that&#x2019;s a great place to stay on your trip. In July and August, visitors get the fantastic opportunity to see the surrounding valley covered in bright purple flowers. The lavender isn&#x2019;t flowering the rest of the year, but Valensole is still a top thing to do in Provence. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/lavender-fields-provence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to see the best lavender fields in Provence<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095734\/provence-Valensole-3-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence things to do valensole\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence things to do valensole\" class=\"wp-image-69768 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095734\/provence-Valensole-3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095734\/provence-Valensole-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095734\/provence-Valensole-3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095734\/provence-Valensole-3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095734\/provence-Valensole-3-109x163.jpg 1