\n<h3 id=\"h-2-oppede\">2. Oppede<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Oppede is straight from the pages of a storybook with its tiny cottages, painted shutters, and narrow lanes. The hilltop village is home to 15th century stone houses, beautiful vineyards, and amazing views of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/lavender-fields-provence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">the lavender fields<\/a>. Believe it or not, this village was once empty! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"oppede provence travel france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"oppede provence travel france\" class=\"wp-image-69787 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-960x1440.jpg 960w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1.jpg 1280w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112355\/provence-oppede-1-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112430\/provence-oppede-4-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"oppede village provence\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"oppede village provence\" class=\"wp-image-69793 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112430\/provence-oppede-4-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112430\/provence-oppede-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112430\/provence-oppede-4-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112430\/provence-oppede-4-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112430\/provence-oppede-4-109x163.jp