ede-2.jpg 1374w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-429x600.jpg 429w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-580x810.jpg 580w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-242x338.jpg 242w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-129x180.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-550x768.jpg 550w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-733x1024.jpg 733w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-773x1080.jpg 773w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-1031x1440.jpg 1031w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-300x419.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-600x838.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2-21x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112408\/provence-oppede-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>After centuries of war, people didn&#x2019;t want to live up high and far away from their farmland. However, during World War 2, the village became inhabited again by artists who loved its charm. We stayed at this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/le-petit-cafe-oppede\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">charming Bed and Breakfast<\/a> in the heart of town. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip<\/strong><em>:<\/em> Hike up to the church and castle at the highest point of the village. Here, you&#x2019;ll see the most spectacular views of the gorge below.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112419\/provence-oppede-3-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence beautiful village oppede\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence beautiful village oppede\" class=\"wp-image-69791 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112419\/provence-oppede-3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112419\/provence-oppede-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112419\/provence-oppede-3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhai