\/provence-oppede-6-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-3-gordes\">3. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/gordes-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Gordes<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s easy to see why this picture-perfect hilltop town has been the setting for famous movies worldwide. The stone houses sit on the edge of the hillside, facing the golden sun and looking down on the luscious green valley below. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2.jpg\" alt=\"provence france gordes viewpoint\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france gordes viewpoint\" class=\"wp-image-69744 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095503\/provence-gordes-2-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2