about:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/gordes-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gordes, France: Icon of Provence<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip: <\/strong>Gordes is also close to some of Provence&#x2019;s most famous lavender fields. For example, the bucket-list photography spot of the Senate Abbey.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence france gordes restaurant\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france gordes restaurant\" class=\"wp-image-69746 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095514\/provence-gordes-3-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\