/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Fontaine-de-Vaucluse is a medieval village known for its spring that flows from a very high cliff. The spring itself sits on a ridge, within a cave, and it&#x2019;s the largest spring in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">France<\/a>! Above the spring, you&#x2019;ll also see the ruins of the ancient local castle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence france fontaine de vaucluse\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france fontaine de vaucluse\" class=\"wp-image-69925 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22100150\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/sta