iver, turning it a beautiful emerald green color. Walk alongside the river as it flows calmly through the village and under bridges, stopping for lunch at one of the lovely riverside cafes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1.jpg\" alt=\"provence france beautiful places Fontaine-de-Vaucluse\"><\/noscript><img width=\"265\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france beautiful places Fontaine-de-Vaucluse\" class=\"wp-image-69795 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1504px) 100vw, 1504px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1.jpg 1504w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-470x600.jpg 470w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-635x810.jpg 635w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-265x338.jpg 265w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-128x163.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-141x180.jpg 141w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-602x768.jpg 602w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-802x1024.jpg 802w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19112437\/provence-Fontaine-de-Vaucluse-1-846x1080.jpg 846w, https:\/\/static.saltinou