e-roussillon-1-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence france things to do \"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france things to do \" class=\"wp-image-69758 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-960x1440.jpg 960w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1.jpg 1280w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-20x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095627\/provence-roussillon-1-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence things to do roussilon\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence things to do roussilon\" class=\"wp-image-69760 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095638\/provence-roussillon-2-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/