 can hire kayaks or paddleboats from a few locations around the gorge. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence france gorges du verdon viewpoint\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france gorges du verdon viewpoint\" class=\"wp-image-69756 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095615\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-4-300x3