\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Enjoy the views from the water, stopping off now and then on riverside beaches, dipping in the river to escape the heat, and feeling the power of the waterfall.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Make sure to check out the viewpoints from the famous bridges nearby. Alternatively, if you have a car, you can drive the loop roads on the top of the gorge, where there are spots to stop and take photos.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Everything about:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/gorges-du-verdon\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Gorges du Verdon, France<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095535\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-1.jpg\" alt=\"provence france gorges du verdon bridge\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france gorges du verdon bridge\" class=\"wp-image-69750 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095535\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095535\/provence-gorges-du-verdon-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095535\/provence-gorges-du-verd