blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cotignac<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cotignac is the secret gem of Provence and relatively undiscovered on the south of France tourist trail. This beautiful cliffside village sits at the bottom of enormous limestone towers and is home to caves that people still live in today! The town is small, but there&#x2019;s plenty to do nearby&#x2014;for example, the local waterfall of Sillans-la-Cascade with its stunning turquoise pools. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/cotignac-all-accommodations\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click to see all the hotels in Cotignac<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"provence france waterfall\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"provence france waterfall\" class=\"wp-image-69738 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/19095429\/provence-cotignac-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.salt